OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fwarm evening with some late sunny then
OL,7,Fclear spells. Generally cloudier
OL,8,Facross Argyll with the risk of mist
OL,9,Fand fog for western coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FEarly morning patchy cloud
OL,12,Fclearing to leave a dry day with
OL,13,Fplenty of warm sunshine.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,16,Fdry with very warm sunshine on
OL,17,FWednesday and Thursday. Cloudier later
OL,18,FThursday into Friday morning with the
OL,19,Frisk of a few showers.
